# рџ“Њ Task Manager App (MERN Stack)

A full-stack Task Manager web application built using **React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB**.  
It allows users to register, login, and manage daily tasks with full CRUD functionality.

---

# рџљЂ Features

## рџ”ђ Authentication
- User Signup and Login
- JWT-based authentication
- Protected routes
- Persistent login using localStorage

---

## рџ“ќ Task Management
- Create tasks with title and description
- Edit existing tasks
- Delete tasks
- Mark tasks as completed or pending
- View all tasks in a clean card layout

---

## рџЋЁ UI / UX
- Responsive design (mobile + desktop)
- Clean dashboard UI
- Task cards layout
- Empty state when no tasks exist
- Toast notifications for actions

---

## вљ™пёЏ Validation
- Signup/Login form validation
- Prevent empty task creation
- Proper error messages for better UX

